PLACEHOLDER — Replace this file with your production Ed25519 public key in PEM format.

To generate a key pair:
  openssl genpkey -algorithm Ed25519 -out urot_privkey_gen1.pem
  openssl pkey -in urot_privkey_gen1.pem -pubout -out urot_pubkey_gen1.pem

The private key (urot_privkey_gen1.pem) must be kept secret and never placed
in this directory or committed to source control.
